<br>
I play a pally and thought I would add a few things .. I know Im badly outnumbered and &quot;The Enemy&quot; here .. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  .. and Im sure Ill get some flames and pally bashing but here goes.<br>
<br>
Pally taunt is very good, and pally stuns generate a lot of hate.  However there is more to tanking than generating aggro, and there is more to maintaining aggro than simply hitting taunt.<br>
<br>
Tanking is about aggro/taunt, damage mitigation, HP's, facing, distance, position and timing.<br>
<br>
As the tank you need to make sure the layout of the area, and where people are situated is to your liking.  Quite simply, everything revolves around the tank, and you are the guy who should be setting things up.<br>
<br>
Ive seen warriors tank very effectivly both in BoT and PoV with pretty standard gear.  Im not saying that warrior taunt is as good as pally SK taunt, but I am saying slightly less aggro doesnt have to slow down xp.  Warriors have better mitigation and HP's, and with good position and by managing the pull, or puller to best advantage I have seen very effective tanking by warriors in these groups.<br>
<br>
Believe me the same slowers that you see getting ressed give a pally tank the same level of stress.  The difference is we have a stun that might save the idiots life, however it doesnt make him any better at what he does, and I wont hesitate to tell them when I want the slow to land.<br>
<br>
Additionally, you guys get the EB weapons, and one of these generates heaps of taunt, and so long as your slower has some brains will work fine.<br>
<br>
Personally in an xp group warrior is fine addition, and I am happy to let them tank (if they know what they are doing, and slower is ok).  In areas where adds are common it lets me do my preferred job of managing adds, and keeping things under control and flowing smoothly.<br>
<br>
However I do like to tank, and know I can make a damn fine job of it.<br>
<br>
I personally think we should collectively (as tanks) be screaming about these damn enchanter and mage pets which are ruining the game, and destroying the need for ALL tanks.<br>
